title: OneKey® MLS Successfully Launches RentSpree Integration for All Subscribers
description: OneKey® MLS, the largest Multiple Listing Service in New York, has launched an integration with RentSpree’s platform to streamline rental transactions. Now, all OneKey MLS subscribers will have access to RentSpree’s ApplyLink™ for new and existing rental listings, cutting down transaction time, limiting liability, increasing efficiency, and keeping the agent central to the rental transaction.
author: Tricia Chirco
name: OneKey® MLS
